snippet.title: Memoriapolis - Launch Date Reveal
snippet.description:
📢 Four Ages. One City. Memoriapolis arrives on April 30, 2025! 
🔗 https://store.steampowered.com/app/2228280/MEMORIAPOLIS/ 

From Antiquity to the Age of Enlightenment, build a city that will stand the test of time! 

Already available on STEAM in EA & watch the full launch trailer in April!

𝗙𝗢𝗨𝗥 𝗔𝗚𝗘𝗦. 𝗢𝗡𝗘 𝗖𝗜𝗧𝗬.
#citybuilder #memoriapolis 

For news and details on Memoriapolis, visit https://playmemoriapolis.com or follow Memoriapolis on social media:
🤍​ Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2228280/MEMORIAPOLIS/
